THE INFAMOUS SMOOTHIE👇🏻:
•handful of ice
•1/2 frozen banana🍌
•1 cup frozen berries (i love blueberry🫐)
•1 scoop protein powder
•1 scoop collagen peptides
•1 tbsp ground flax seeds
•1 tbsp chia seeds
•1 tbsp MCT oil
•big a$$ spoonfuls of peanut or almond butter🥜🍯
•handful of spinach🥝 
•water or nut milk for desired thickness

blend until creamy and smooth. if you’re me add some granola on top!!! 

#smoothierecipes #smoothie #glutenfree #dairyfree
